title: Darkness (Full Song on Tape Cassette)
description:
Watch the remix process here: https://youtu.be/j3GjU0oQHJE
Tape master of Darkness remix, done on Type I cassette on my dad's old tape deck. I didn't use the deck's Dolby noise reduction; it attenuates the highs too much to be enjoyable. I kinda like the noise anyway
